\p 
\v 15 \w It|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w in|strong="G2532"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w confidence|strong="G4006"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* planning \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w by|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w first|strong="G4386"\w*,
\v 16 \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w by|strong="G1223"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* proceed \w into|strong="G1519"\w* \w Macedonia|strong="G3109"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w back|strong="G3825"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w from|strong="G2064"\w* \w Macedonia|strong="G3109"\w* (\w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w might|strong="G2532"\w* \w benefit|strong="G1519"\w* twice),\f + \fr 1:16 \ft The “benefit” is presumably spiritual; Paul seems to be saying that he imparts such benefit wherever he goes. I would like to be able to say the same thing.\f* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w then|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w sent|strong="G2532"\w* \w by|strong="G1223"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w my|strong="G5259"\w* \w way|strong="G4311"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w Judea|strong="G2449"\w*.\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Here Paul is probably referring to financial help.\f*
\v 17 \w Now|strong="G2532"\w* \w then|strong="G3767"\w*, \w when|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w was|strong="G1510"\w* deciding \w this|strong="G3778"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w was|strong="G1510"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* acting frivolously, \w was|strong="G1510"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w*? \w Or|strong="G2228"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w things|strong="G3778"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* decide, \w do|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* decide \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w flesh|strong="G4561"\w*, \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w with|strong="G3844"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w would|strong="G1014"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* \w both|strong="G2532"\w* “\w Yes|strong="G3483"\w*, \w yes|strong="G3483"\w*” \w and|strong="G2532"\w* “\w No|strong="G3756"\w*, \w no|strong="G3756"\w*”?
