\v 19 \w because|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Son|strong="G5207"\w* \w of|strong="G5207"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*, \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*, \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w was|strong="G1096"\w* \w proclaimed|strong="G2784"\w* \w among|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w by|strong="G1223"\w* \w us|strong="G2249"\w*—\w by|strong="G1223"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w Silvanus|strong="G4610"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w Timothy|strong="G5095"\w*\f + \fr 1:19 \ft Paul gives credit to his associates.\f*—\w was|strong="G1096"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* “\w Yes|strong="G3483"\w*” \w and|strong="G2532"\w* “\w No|strong="G3756"\w*”. \w In|strong="G1722"\w* fact, \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w has|strong="G2316"\w* \it always\it* \w been|strong="G1096"\w* “\w Yes|strong="G3483"\w*”,
\v 20 \w because|strong="G1223"\w* \w all|strong="G3745"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w promises|strong="G1860"\w* \w of|strong="G1223"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* “\w Yes|strong="G3483"\w*”; \w indeed|strong="G2532"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* “Amen”, \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w glory|strong="G1391"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w through|strong="G1223"\w* \w us|strong="G2249"\w*.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft As we take advantage of the promises, God gets the glory. God's promises are positive, with the ‘yes’.\f*
\v 21 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* establishes \w us|strong="G1519"\w* \w together|strong="G4862"\w* \w with|strong="G4862"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w into|strong="G1519"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w anointed|strong="G5548"\w*\f + \fr 1:21 \ft The anointing is in the past, but the establishing is an ongoing process—note that it is “\nd into\nd*” Christ.\f* \w us|strong="G1519"\w*, \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*,
\v 22 \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w also|strong="G2532"\w* \w sealed|strong="G4972"\w* \w us|strong="G1325"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w gave|strong="G1325"\w* \w us|strong="G1325"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* down payment \w of|strong="G4151"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Spirit|strong="G4151"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w our|strong="G2532"\w* \w hearts|strong="G2588"\w*.\f + \fr 1:22 \ft The Holy Spirit in us is like God's brand on us, but is also our guarantee that we have been regenerated. Verses 21-22 refer to all three persons of the Godhead.\f*
\s2 The change explained
\p 
\v 23 \w For|strong="G3754"\w* \w my|strong="G1699"\w* \w part|strong="G1473"\w*, \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w call|strong="G1941"\w* \w on|strong="G1909"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w as|strong="G1519"\w* \w witness|strong="G3144"\w*, \w upon|strong="G1909"\w* \w my|strong="G1699"\w* \w soul|strong="G5590"\w*, \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w it|strong="G3754"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w spare|strong="G5339"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w have|strong="G1473"\w* \w not|strong="G3765"\w* \w yet|strong="G1161"\w* \w returned|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w Corinth|strong="G2882"\w*.
\v 24 (\w Not|strong="G3756"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w we|strong="G3754"\w* \w have|strong="G3748"\w* control \w over|strong="G2961"\w* \w your|strong="G3588"\w* \w faith|strong="G4102"\w*,\f + \fr 1:24 \ft This is an important point: in Matthew 23:8-10 the Lord Jesus forbids any attempt to dominate someone else's faith or conscience. As He said to the Samaritan woman, the Father wants worship in spirit and truth (John 4:23-24)—the worship must not be faked, forced or controlled.\f* \w but|strong="G1063"\w* \w we|strong="G3754"\w* work \w with|strong="G3756"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w your|strong="G3588"\w* \w joy|strong="G5479"\w*, \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G3754"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w by|strong="G2476"\w* \w faith|strong="G4102"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w stand|strong="G2476"\w* \w firm|strong="G2476"\w*.)
\c 2
\m 
\v 1 \w Actually|strong="G1063"\w*, \w I|strong="G1161"\w* \w determined|strong="G2919"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w within|strong="G1722"\w* \w myself|strong="G1683"\w*, \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w I|strong="G1161"\w* \w would|strong="G2064"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w again|strong="G3825"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w sorrow|strong="G3077"\w*.
\v 2 \w For|strong="G1063"\w* \w if|strong="G1487"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w make|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w sorrowful|strong="G3076"\w*, \w then|strong="G2532"\w* \w who|strong="G5101"\w* \w will|strong="G5101"\w* \w make|strong="G2532"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w glad|strong="G2165"\w*, \w besides|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w whom|strong="G5101"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w made|strong="G3076"\w* \w sorrowful|strong="G3076"\w*?
