\v 10 \w The|strong="G1722"\w* truth \w of|strong="G1722"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*: \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w boasting|strong="G2746"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* silenced \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w regions|strong="G2824"\w* \w of|strong="G1722"\w* Achaia.
