\s2 The ‘thorn in the flesh’
\p 
\v 7 \w Because|strong="G2532"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* incredible importance \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* revelations, \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w keep|strong="G3361"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* feeling \w too|strong="G2532"\w* important, \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w given|strong="G1325"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w thorn|strong="G4647"\w* \w in|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w flesh|strong="G4561"\w*, \w a|strong="G2532"\w* messenger \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w Satan|strong="G4567"\w*\f + \fr 12:7 \ft ‘Satan’ is Satan. Down through human history God has always used Satan, demons and evil men, both to punish evil and to restrain it (usually in those who are evil). Here God does so with Paul before the fact, that is, to forestall the sin. The procedure was sufficiently unusual that God actually explained to Paul why He did it.\f* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w beat|strong="G2852"\w* \w on|strong="G2443"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w*—\w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w keep|strong="G3361"\w* \w me|strong="G1325"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* feeling \w too|strong="G2532"\w* important.
\v 8 \w Concerning|strong="G5228"\w* \w this|strong="G3778"\w* \w thing|strong="G3778"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w pleaded|strong="G3870"\w* \w with|strong="G2962"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w Lord|strong="G2962"\w* \w three|strong="G5151"\w* \w times|strong="G5151"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w it|strong="G3778"\w* \w might|strong="G3778"\w* depart \w from|strong="G3588"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*.
\v 9 \w But|strong="G2532"\w* \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w said|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*, “\w My|strong="G1722"\w* \w grace|strong="G5485"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* sufficient \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w*, \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w my|strong="G1722"\w* \w power|strong="G1411"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w made|strong="G3004"\w* perfect \w in|strong="G1722"\w* weakness.” \w Therefore|strong="G3767"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w will|strong="G2532"\w* \w boast|strong="G2744"\w* \w all|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w more|strong="G3123"\w* cheerfully \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w my|strong="G1722"\w* weaknesses, \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*'s \w power|strong="G1411"\w* \w may|strong="G2532"\w* \w take|strong="G3123"\w* \w up|strong="G5055"\w* residence \w upon|strong="G1909"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*.\f + \fr 12:9 \ft That is what the Text says, ‘take up residence’. I would say that for most of us unusual manifestations of God's power are sporadic (if there are any at all)—if the power ‘takes up residence’, the manifestations should be a regular occurrence. The trouble is, there is evidently a considerable price in suffering that must be paid.\f*
\v 10 \w So|strong="G2532"\w* \w then|strong="G2532"\w*, \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w take|strong="G2106"\w* \w pleasure|strong="G2106"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* weaknesses,\f + \fr 12:10 \ft Well, I must confess that I have not gotten there yet.\f* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w insults|strong="G5196"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* hardships, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w persecutions|strong="G1375"\w*, \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w distresses|strong="G4730"\w*, \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*'s \w sake|strong="G5228"\w*. \w For|strong="G1063"\w* \w when|strong="G3752"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G1510"\w* weak, \w then|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G1510"\w* \w strong|strong="G1415"\w*.
\s1 Apostolic signs were produced
\p 
\v 11 \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* boasting foolishly, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* drove \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w*. \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w ought|strong="G3784"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* \w commended|strong="G4921"\w* \w by|strong="G5259"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w because|strong="G1063"\w* \w in|strong="G2532"\w* \w nothing|strong="G3762"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w been|strong="G1510"\w* \w inferior|strong="G5302"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w very|strong="G3029"\w* best apostles, \w though|strong="G1487"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w am|strong="G1510"\w* \w nothing|strong="G3762"\w*.
